Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.99,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs17}室外\N野营\N登山用品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:11.41,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(460,312)\fad(0,3)}Schlaf是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是登山道具店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是宝山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有便携小锅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钛制的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好轻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Schlaf是指睡袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  要7万円
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么轻便
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高挑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我是一个学校的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我点建议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个1万8千円的睡袋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这个2万4千円的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪个比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:00:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实际上是准备带着帐篷和睡袋去「纵走」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「纵走」？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一边露营一边攀登几座山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是现在正犹豫要买哪个睡袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么区别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是重量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.91,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}化学纤维制\N重\N体积大\N便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要背一整天所以重量很关键
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:22.07,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}羽绒制\N轻\N便携\N高价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然打工攒了不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样一来预算就很吃紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在犹豫也就意味着其实想要贵的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么回答才能让她满意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其放弃并妥协
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得就算会后悔还是不妥协比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  谢谢你推了我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去结账
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她满意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也登山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一瞬间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就这么回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就是山友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换一下邮箱地址吧  我叫齐藤枫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向  我啊  其实很不擅长和人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  事到如今还说这个干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的这么干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你自己注意到了这不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,80)\fs21\frz-19}上次多谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看  是枫同学发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又交到了一个朋友
